Well I sleep on me grandma's floor in her bedroom on the mattresses me mother used to carry 'em round - with - one of neighbours used to h
elp me mother to carry the mattresses round and we had them on my mother's - me grandmother's floor while me mother did her week and then they were brought back at weekend when me mother was on days. Because me mother wouldn't leave us in't house by ourse
lves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8336051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14909196\charrsid11677679 Before that you used to eat at your grannies when you were at school?
