s and I think I were only one in Bradford that had me grandma's apron for a Whitsuntide dress. That's God's truth. That is. I haven't tell a lie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8336051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14909196\charrsid11677679 You didn't share the house at Stanacre place with anybody?
