\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8336051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14909196\charrsid11677679 Do you remember what hours your mother worked when she was in the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15404701 EY  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14909196\charrsid11677679 Yes, from half past six on the morning to five at - at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8336051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14909196\charrsid11677679 And then she had to come home with her family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15404701 EY  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14909196\charrsid11677679 That's right, yes. And we had to help her with all our jobs to do - she gave us each a job and we'd to do it - even lads had to do it.

