t - you know - bring coal up or chop wood and things like that it - and it - it's helped many a time to wash me mother's floor. You know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8336051 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14909196\charrsid11677679 The washing was done at home was it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15404701 EY  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14909196\charrsid11677679 Yes, it was done at home was the - was the washing. And also ironing 
