 but he helped to bath us because the girls were bathed the first and then the boys was bathed the second because - girls all had long hair, you know, the - and he used to dry hair for you while me mother was - and then it was a matter of the water beatin
g us - we'd only a gas stove you know, there were - and side boiler and we'd - so - sort of - we had to have our bath in same water because it - it were a matter of - you know - gas and things like that.
